Package amiller.colormap

Class Summary
ColorChooserDialog A modal dialog for choosing a color.
ColorMap This class represents a function over [0,1] that generates an ordered list of colors.
ColorMapChooser A panel with a list of color maps to choose from.
ColorMapSequence A ColorMapSequence is a colormap representing the sequence of two or more source colormaps.
ColorMapViewer A canvas for displaying a ColorMap (from left to right).
Main This is a test harness for ColorMaps.
NaturalSpectrum The natural spectrum ColorMap - ROYGBIV.
ParametricColorMap This class represents a parametric ColorMap with curves for red, green and blue with height, slope, location, and vertical offset.
ParametricFunction This class represents a ParametricColorMap function (in one color) with peak height, peak slope, horizontal position, and vertical offset.
PropertyConfigurator Configures a view from a resource bundle.
TwoColorBlend  
TwoColorBlendEditor A panel for editing a TwoColorBlend colormap.
